---
title: Smart Blueberry-Dressed Tofu Salad with Almond Pralines
description: This summery salad is simple and tasty any time of the year! Mixed greens are tossed with a stellar blueberry vinaigrette, while pan-fried tofu brings a filling protein hit. Plus who can say no to sweet and crunchy almond pralines to top things off?!

Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie and carbohydrate amount.
